<sn>1.</sn> <def>a pair of slender sticks made of wood, ivory, plastic,
etc., used chiefly by the Chinese and Japanese to lift food into the
mouth while dining; -- also commonly used around the world by persons of
Oriental heritage or in restaurants serving oriental food.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

